4
00:00:10,894 --> 00:00:12,093
"White Spirits, Kuda Pacu" -Beberapa hari kemudian,

5
00:00:12,094 --> 00:00:16,093
"Kozo Tokuyoshi (55), Pemilik Kuda" -White Spirits dibawa

6
