21
00:02:44,981 --> 00:02:50,684
"Kasus Penculikan Thoroughbred (Bagian 2)"

22
00:03:03,781 --> 00:03:05,981
"White Spirits."

23
00:03:09,645 --> 00:03:11,744
Aku yakin, inspektur.

24
00:03:11,745 --> 00:03:15,345
